<template><section>

<h2 id="input"><a class="header-anchor" href="#input" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Input</h2>
<p>Input data using mouse or keyboard.</p>
<h3 id="basic-usage"><a class="header-anchor" href="#basic-usage" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Basic usage</h3>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-input&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      input: ''\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-input placeholder="Please input" v-model="input"></el-input>


</div>
                    
                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"input"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>

<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> {
  data() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {
      <span class="hljs-attr">input</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
    }
  }
}
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="disabled"><a class="header-anchor" href="#disabled" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Disabled</h3>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input1\&quot; :disabled=\&quot;true\&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/el-input&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      input1: ''\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-input placeholder="Please input" v-model="input1" :disabled="true">
</el-input>


</div>
                    <p>Disable the Input with the <code>disabled</code> attribute.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"input1"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">:disabled</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"true"</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>

<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> {
  data() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {
      <span class="hljs-attr">input1</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
    }
  }
}
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="input-with-icon"><a class="header-anchor" href="#input-with-icon" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Input with icon</h3>
<p>Add an icon to indicate input type.</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Pick a date\&quot; icon=\&quot;search\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input2\&quot; :on-icon-click=\&quot;handleIconClick\&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/el-input&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      input2: ''\n    }\n  },\n  methods: {\n    handleIconClick(ev) {\n      console.log(ev);\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-input placeholder="Pick a date" icon="search" v-model="input2" :on-icon-click="handleIconClick">
</el-input>


</div>
                    <p>You can add an icon at the end of Input by setting the <code>icon</code> attribute and use <code>on-icon-click</code> hook to complete some work after clicking the icon.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Pick a date"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">icon</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"search"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"input2"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">:on-icon-click</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"handleIconClick"</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>

<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> {
  data() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {
      <span class="hljs-attr">input2</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
    }
  },
  <span class="hljs-attr">methods</span>: {
    handleIconClick(ev) {
      <span class="hljs-built_in">console</span>.log(ev);
    }
  }
}
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="textarea"><a class="header-anchor" href="#textarea" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Textarea</h3>
<p>Resizable for entering multiple lines of text information. Add attribute <code>type=&quot;textarea&quot;</code> to change <code>input</code> into native <code>textarea</code>.</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-input type=\&quot;textarea\&quot; :rows=\&quot;2\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;textarea\&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/el-input&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      textarea: ''\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-input type="textarea" :rows="2" placeholder="Please input" v-model="textarea">
</el-input>


</div>
                    <p>Control the height by setting the <code>rows</code> prop.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"textarea"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">:rows</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"2"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"textarea"</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>

<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> {
  data() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {
      <span class="hljs-attr">textarea</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
    }
  }
}
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="autosize-textarea"><a class="header-anchor" href="#autosize-textarea" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Autosize Textarea</h3>
<p>Setting the <code>autosize</code> prop for a textarea type of Input makes the height to automatically adjust based on the content. An options object can be provided to <code>autosize</code> to specify the minimum and maximum number of lines the textarea can automatically adjust.</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-input type=\&quot;textarea\&quot; autosize placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;textarea2\&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/el-input&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&quot;margin: 20px 0;\&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;el-input type=\&quot;textarea\&quot; :autosize=\&quot;{ minRows: 2, maxRows: 4}\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;textarea3\&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/el-input&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      textarea2: '',\n      textarea3: ''\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-input type="textarea" autosize="" placeholder="Please input" v-model="textarea2">
</el-input>
<div style="margin: 20px 0;"></div>
<el-input type="textarea" :autosize="{ minRows: 2, maxRows: 4}" placeholder="Please input" v-model="textarea3">
</el-input>


</div>
                    
                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"textarea"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">autosize</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"textarea2"</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"margin: 20px 0;"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"textarea"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">:autosize</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"{ minRows: 2, maxRows: 4}"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"textarea3"</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>

<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> {
  data() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {
      <span class="hljs-attr">textarea2</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>,
      <span class="hljs-attr">textarea3</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
    }
  }
}
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="mixed-input"><a class="header-anchor" href="#mixed-input" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Mixed input</h3>
<p>Prepend or append an element, generally a label or a button.</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;div&gt;\n  &lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input3\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;template slot=\&quot;prepend\&quot;&gt;Http://&lt;/template&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&quot;margin-top: 15px;\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input4\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;template slot=\&quot;append\&quot;&gt;.com&lt;/template&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=\&quot;margin-top: 15px;\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Please input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input5\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;el-select v-model=\&quot;select\&quot; slot=\&quot;prepend\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Select\&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;el-option label=\&quot;Restaurant\&quot; value=\&quot;1\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-option&gt;\n      &lt;el-option label=\&quot;Order No.\&quot; value=\&quot;2\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-option&gt;\n      &lt;el-option label=\&quot;Tel\&quot; value=\&quot;3\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-option&gt;\n    &lt;/el-select&gt;\n    &lt;el-button slot=\&quot;append\&quot; icon=\&quot;search\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-button&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      input3: '',\n      input4: '',\n      input5: '',\n      select: ''\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;\n  .el-select .el-input {\n    width: 110px;\n  }\n&quot;}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><div>
  <el-input placeholder="Please input" v-model="input3">
    <template slot="prepend">Http://</template>
  </el-input>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: 15px;">
  <el-input placeholder="Please input" v-model="input4">
    <template slot="append">.com</template>
  </el-input>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: 15px;">
  <el-input placeholder="Please input" v-model="input5">
    <el-select v-model="select" slot="prepend" placeholder="Select">
      <el-option label="Restaurant" value="1"></el-option>
      <el-option label="Order No." value="2"></el-option>
      <el-option label="Tel" value="3"></el-option>
    </el-select>
    <el-button slot="append" icon="search"></el-button>
  </el-input>
</div>



</div>
                    <p>Use <code>slot</code> to distribute elements that prepend or append to Input.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"input3"</span>&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">template</span> <span class="hljs-attr">slot</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"prepend"</span>&gt;</span>Http://<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">template</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"margin-top: 15px;"</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"input4"</span>&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">template</span> <span class="hljs-attr">slot</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"append"</span>&gt;</span>.com<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">template</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"margin-top: 15px;"</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Please input"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"input5"</span>&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-select</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"select"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">slot</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"prepend"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Select"</span>&gt;</span>
      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span> <span class="hljs-attr">label</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Restaurant"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"1"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span>&gt;</span>
      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span> <span class="hljs-attr">label</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Order No."</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"2"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span>&gt;</span>
      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span> <span class="hljs-attr">label</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"Tel"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"3"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-option</span>&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-select</span>&gt;</span>
    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-button</span> <span class="hljs-attr">slot</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"append"</span> <span class="hljs-attr">icon</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"search"</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-button</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-input</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span>

<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="css">
  <span class="hljs-selector-class">.el-select</span> <span class="hljs-selector-class">.el-input</span> {
    <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>: <span class="hljs-number">110px</span>;
  }
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">style</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript">
<span class="hljs-keyword">export</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> {
  data() {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> {
      <span class="hljs-attr">input3</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>,
      <span class="hljs-attr">input4</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>,
      <span class="hljs-attr">input5</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>,
      <span class="hljs-attr">select</span>: <span class="hljs-string">''</span>
    }
  }
}
</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="sizes"><a class="header-anchor" href="#sizes" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Sizes</h3>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;div class=\&quot;demo-input-size\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-input size=\&quot;large\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Please Input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input6\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n  &lt;el-input placeholder=\&quot;Please Input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input7\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n  &lt;el-input size=\&quot;small\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Please Input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input8\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n  &lt;el-input size=\&quot;mini\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Please Input\&quot; v-model=\&quot;input9\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;/el-input&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\nexport default {\n  data() {\n    return {\n      input6: '',\n      input7: '',\n      input8: '',\n      input9: ''\n    }\n  }\n}\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
