</div>
                    <p>Add <code>size</code> attribute to change the size of Input. In addition to the default size, there are three other options: <code>large</code>, <code>small</code> and <code>mini</code>.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"demo-input-size"</span>&gt;</span>
